text: To himself everyone is immortal; he may know that he is going to die, but he can never know he is dead.
author: Samuel Butler

text: Follow your instincts. That is where true wisdom manifests itself.
author: Oprah Winfrey

text: I believe that potential is unlimited - success depends on daring to act on dreams.
author: Estee Lauder

text: Everyone has the right to make his own decisions, but none has the right to force his decision on others.
author: Ayn Rand

text: Whenever people agree with me I always feel I must be wrong.
author: Oscar Wilde
